# GearTrack

**GearTrack** is a modern, Mac-friendly equipment management app for checking in/out gear, tracking users, printing barcode/QR labels, and keeping secure, detailed logs.

## ğŸš€ Features
- Check-in/check-out items
- Admin/user management (secure login, inactivity logout)
- Notes, image uploads, asset status (good/worn/needs repair)
- Print/export barcode and QR labels (with date in service and all fields)
- Kiosk mode (admin-only exit)
- Export filtered reports (CSV, PDF)
- Custom branding

